vulnerabilities.title: Prototype Pollution in deep-get-set
vulnerabilities.description: All versions of package deep-get-set prior to version 1.1.1 are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution via the main function.

vulnerabilities.title: Prototype Pollution in deep-get-set
vulnerabilities.description: All versions of package deep-get-set are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution via the 'deep' function. **Note:** This vulnerability derives from an incomplete fix of [CVE-2020-7715](https://security.snyk.io/vuln/SNYK-JS-DEEPGETSET-598666)
